	<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Rivtech</h1>
	
	<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
		<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">From The Cataclysm: Dark Days Ahead Wiki</div>
		<div id="contentSub"></div>
		
		
		
		<div id="jump-to-nav"></div>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#mw-head">Jump to navigation</a>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#p-search">Jump to search</a>
		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><p><b>Rivtech</b> is a private defense contractor that primarily makes weapons, but it seems they also produce atomic powered consumer goods, including <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Atomic_nightlight" title="Atomic nightlight">atomic nightlight</a>, <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Atomic_lamp" title="Atomic lamp">atomic lamp</a>, <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Atomic_coffee_maker" title="Atomic coffee maker">atomic coffee maker</a>, and an energy drink.
</p><p><br />
</p>
<dl><dt>Name</dt>
<dd>Rivtech</dd>
<dt>Type</dt>
<dd>Brand</dd>
<dt>Members</dt>
<dd></dd></dl>
